PrecisRe-appointment of AUGUSTE CHOQUETTE, of Montreal, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour, for a term of five years, effective January 18, 1996.
